   <body>
      <p>Power Invoice Generation for Salesforce Billing includes all of the features and functionality of Power Composer with the following exceptions:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Customers can only generate documents from the objects within the Salesforce Billing installed package (those with the blng prefix).</li>
         <li>Word and HTML Email are the only supported template types.</li>
         <li>Email and PDF are the only output file types.</li>
         <li>Up to 1,000 free invoices per month. Additional service events can be purchased.</li>
         <li>Product support is provided by Salesforce CPQ (not Power directly),</li>
         <li>The output document will include "Powered by Power" in red letters, in the document footer</li>
      </ul>
